name: 安娜·梅·奎恩
name_full: 安娜·梅·奎恩 Anna Mae Quinn
introduction: Anna Mae's screen debut was in the film, A Carolina Christmas (2020). Her breakthrough role was as Prada Lamonca on season 1 of Peacock's comedy series, Killing It, starring Craig Robinson (2022). Anna Mae's role of Prada was brought back for 4 episodes in season 2 (2023). Anna Mae keeps her performing skills sharp by acting year-round in community theater and taking dialect, voice, guitar and drum lessons.
